"<shortcut> &Del; </shortcut> <guimenu>إجراءات</guimenu> <guimenuitem>احذف</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:3351
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose <guilabel>Delete</guilabel> to <action>remove the currently selected "
"journal entry, event or to-do.</action>"
